headline: Carrier Introduces AquaEdge® 30CF Chiller to Enhance Data Center Reliability and Uptime
summary: Carrier today introduced the AquaEdge® 30CF air-cooled centrifugal chiller, designed to help data center operators maintain continuous cooling performance and protect uptime under real-world operating conditions. Carrier is a part of Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR), global leader in intelligent climate and energy solutions.

headline: 3 Overrated  Stocks That Fall Short
